Package org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.util.conversion

Class TimeConverter<N extends Number>

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.util.conversion.TimeConverter<N>
Direct Known Subclasses:
TimeConverter.DoubleTimeConverter, TimeConverter.LongTimeConverter
public abstract class TimeConverter<N extends Number> extends Object
Adapter for JSON fields which translates values as string representatives to actual long or double values (nanoseconds), e.g., "10 ms" -> 10_000_000, "20 ns" -> 20, "0.5h" -> 1_800_000_000_000
